query:
INSERT INTO
                        categories (id, created_at, sort_key, title, `order`, user_id, track, show_in_lib, deleted_at)
                    VALUES
                        (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
                    ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
                        created_at = ?,
                        sort_key = ?,
                        title = ?,
                        `order` = ?,
                        user_id = ?,
                        track = ?,
                        show_in_lib = ?,
                        deleted_at = ?
